+    //    For least squares there are several decomposition methods:
+    //       DECOMP_LU
+    //       DECOMP_CHOLESKY ([A] must be symmetrical)
+    //       DECOMP_EIG ([A] must be symmetrical)
+    //       DECOMP_SVD
+    //       DECOMP_QR
